        <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/72">
          30 minutes on your specific situation. No pitch, no deck, no trying-to-close. You'll leave with a clearer read on your biggest growth bottleneck and whether working together makes sense. If it doesn't, I'll tell you what I'd do instead.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <a class="button-accent" href={ctas.primary.href} data-cta="final-primary">{ctas.primary.label} →</a>
          <a class="button-link-invert" href={ctas.caseStudies.href} data-cta="final-case-studies">{ctas.caseStudies.label} →</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
          Prefer email first? <a class="text-white underline" href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}>{siteConfig.email}</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

